        "sl_atr_mult": 1.0,
        "rationale": "Trend-continuation archetype requires R:R >= 2.5; with rv_20 at the 89th percentile the fat left tail (return IQR down to 0.162) pays asymmetric shorts, and the wide ATR unit at this vol level makes a 1-ATR stop survivable against stressed-regime noise while the 3-ATR target harvests continuation legs."
